{"tid":969284,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"玩密室逃脫遇上火災　波蘭5女無法逃脫被燒死","createTime":"2019-01-05T02:53:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-24T20:34:22.000Z","uid":32511,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"9eecafd620ec9156769b6d68d3ef68de732a808e","tid":969284,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T02:53:56.000Z","msg":"波蘭北部市科沙林（Koszalin）的一個「密室逃脫」遊戲場，周五（4日）下午發生火災，結果造成5名女子喪生，她們年僅15至20歲，另有一名年約25歲的男子嚴重燒傷。目前尚不清楚起火的原因。<br />\n <br />\n消防隊表示，大火發生於下午5時許，當時死者們正在參加生日派對，但碰巧遇上大火，她們因為逃不出密室，全被燒死。<br />\n <br />\n「密室逃脫」遊戲，是一種真人體驗，參加者會被困在一個封閉的空間，必須在有限的時間內，解決各種難題，才能找到逃離的鑰匙、方法。波蘭有超過一千個地點提供這類遊戲。"},{"pid":"41e8105cc5b44ab44f5dbcd5d111b2a3254ab2fa","tid":969284,"uid":57226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T02:56:16.000Z","msg":"柯南題材"},{"pid":"3a7d6bdb4ee0c350cf10e0bf99c486df76f3ec4a","tid":969284,"uid":53105,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T02:58:14.000Z","msg":"好真實<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13cb2337fdc72abb5fbde8f2f766c51b2d0b975f","tid":969284,"uid":17103,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T02:59:51.000Z","msg":"玩過咁多次真係冇諗過會火燭"},{"pid":"95ae2296105af00f7dabcbaa9652c878b1d60487","tid":969284,"uid":11067,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T03:03:56.000Z","msg":"wanna play a game"},{"pid":"38d39c3e895a5abfe78c98f8fed75e861e906524","tid":969284,"uid":53632,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3a7d6bdb4ee0c350cf10e0bf99c486df76f3ec4a","tid":969284,"uid":53105,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T02:58:14.000Z","msg":"好真實<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T03:05:55.000Z","msg":"解唔到真係會死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c6d626875af5ff1e6574cda12636d244710a0c4","tid":9